            <td>policy on placement of a right curly brace (<code>'}'</code>)</td>
            <td><a href="property_types.html#rcurly">right curly brace policy</a></td>
            <td><code>same</code></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>shouldStartLine</td>
            <td>should we check if <code>'}'</code>
            starts line.</td>
